  "title": "BEAUTICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform skin and body analysis for new and existing customers.</li><li>Exposures to a diverse range of beauty treatments, including skin, face, body, slimming, hair removal, skin whitening etc.</li><li>Carry out treatment according to company standard operating procedure and service standard.</li><li>Responsible for housekeeping, maintenance and cleanliness of the Branch Attentive to customer's needs at all times.</li><li>Makes professional recommendations on products, treatments to customers.</li><li>Handle customer enquiries, requests and booking of appointments.</li><li>Able to establish long term customer relationship.</li><li>Related experience as a Beautician is an advantage.</li><li>Attractive Salary, Bonus, Allowances, Incentive.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Qualified with working experience, preferably in relevant industry.</li><li>Willingness to learn and demonstrates a positive working attitude.</li><li>Well-groomed, hygienic, and presentable at all times.</li><li>Experience in beauty services.</li></ul>",
